OL,3,CState pension and benefits rise: How
OL,4,Ccould the changes affect you?
OL,6,FMillions of people will see their
OL,7,Fstate pensions and benefits rise on
OL,8,FMonday as a new tax year begins.
OL,10,FState pensions will go up by 8.5%,
OL,11,Fmeaning some pensioners will receive
OL,12,Fan extra #900 per year.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, those on Universal Credit
OL,15,Fwill see their payments rise by 6.7%
OL,16,Falong with a number of other benefits.
