OL,3,CState pension and benefits rise: How
OL,4,Ccould the changes affect you?
OL,6,FThe government says it is putting
OL,7,Fmoney back into the pockets of
OL,8,Fpensioners, but there are concerns
OL,9,Fhundreds of thousands of them may be
OL,10,Fdragged into paying tax for the first
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,FWho qualifies for the pension rise?
OL,15,FState pension has gone up by 8.5% as
OL,16,Fof this week.
OL,18,FThose who retired after 2016, who have
OL,19,Fthe full new state pension will see
OL,20,Ftheir payments rise to #11,502 this
OL,21,Ftax year.
