OL,3,CState pension and benefits rise: How
OL,4,Ccould the changes affect you?
OL,6,FThe basic state pension, which is paid
OL,7,Fto those who reach state pension age
OL,8,Fbefore April 2016, is going to rise to
OL,9,F#8,814.
OL,11,FWill all pensioners who qualify
OL,12,Factually be better off from today?
OL,14,FCurrently, pensioners can have the
OL,15,Fmoney tax-free up to #12,750.
