OL,3,CState pension and benefits rise: How
OL,4,Ccould the changes affect you?
OL,6,FThose on the the new full basic state
OL,7,Fpension, are already on more than
OL,8,F#11,000 a year, so if they have an
OL,9,Fadditional income, perhaps a company
OL,10,For personal pension, they will be
OL,11,Fpaying tax on their income.
OL,13,FUniversal Credit
OL,15,FUniversal Credit claimants will
OL,16,Freceive a 6.7% increase, a rise which
OL,17,Fextends to other benefits including
OL,18,Fthe personal independence payment,
OL,19,Fdisability living allowance and
OL,20,Femployment and support allowance.
