OL,3,CState pension and benefits rise: How
OL,4,Ccould the changes affect you?
OL,6,FThe amount people receive varies
OL,7,Fdepending on circumstance, single
OL,8,Fpeople aged under 25 will now be
OL,9,Fgetting #311, as opposed to the old
OL,10,Frate, which was #292 per month.
OL,12,FBut for example, if you're joint
OL,13,Fclaimants and you're both aged over 25
OL,14,Fand over, then you'll be getting #617
OL,15,Fper month, and that's up from #576.
